description:
This is a 24 minute workout called '20 MIN EXPRESS PILATES WORKOUT || Beginner to Moderate Pilates (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.
